{"tid":1657423,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"有咩建議畀加泰人？","createTime":"2019-10-16T05:31:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T10:05:17.000Z","uid":182047,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"925ac7032e6630bad1deca1ff8316e7139f3650b","tid":1657423,"uid":182047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:31:28.000Z","msg":"多用快閃遊擊，避免被捕。<br />\n<br />\n有手足被拉，唔好企定定做觀眾，要救人。<br />\n<br />\n和勇合一，核爆都唔割。用和平畫面爭取國際支持，但不可與勇武切割。<br />\n<br />\n要爭取民意支持，盡力打好宣傳戰。唔好忘記你哋都係民意一部分，比起盲從民意，更要想辦法帶領民意。沒有一場革命是做完民意調查才進行的。<br />\n<br />\n外國支持係重要，但唔好以為外國講兩句就會有實質幫助。任何國家都係睇利益行事。<br />\n<br />\n歡迎補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6ace1a8928b2c6817820ef5bf1179eaca85a4e1","tid":1657423,"uid":185184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:32:01.000Z","msg":"be water"},{"pid":"8257427e7926a5615d2251a9cc4cc8c699dd78af","tid":1657423,"uid":167102,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:32:19.000Z","msg":"你講嗰啲我哋都未做得好點教人"},{"pid":"674480a80313bcdad23e3f4fa39f5563ebe7fc09","tid":1657423,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:34:14.000Z","msg":"唔好痴埋黎 我地唔搞獨立"},{"pid":"a203c5637d23f9d5891631eead0b5fd143eb98d4","tid":1657423,"uid":201414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:34:29.000Z","msg":"on9搞掂自己地方先啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60d9e0239b71221d22e9c54494a6f26b5aa2e0e","tid":1657423,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:36:49.000Z","msg":"dont be hong kong , be better"},{"pid":"7db7c7bb8a456116cf80f3671c4288e59ab3d3ba","tid":1657423,"uid":163207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"674480a80313bcdad23e3f4fa39f5563ebe7fc09","tid":1657423,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T05:34:14.000Z","msg":"唔好痴埋黎 我地唔搞獨立"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T10: